OL,3,CMore Guernsey islanders are making the
OL,4,Cswitch to full-fat milk
OL,6,FMore Guernsey residents are making the
OL,7,Fswitch to Full-Cream milk, according
OL,8,Fto a recent island-wide survey.
OL,10,FAround 2,400 islanders participated in
OL,11,Fthe Island Global Research survey,
OL,12,Flast conducted in 2019.
OL,14,FIt found a 43.75% rise in the number
OL,15,Fof Guernsey residents choosing full-
OL,16,Ffat (red carton) milk between 2019 and
OL,17,Fthis year.
