OL,3,CMore Guernsey islanders are making the
OL,4,Cswitch to full-fat milk
OL,6,FIt follows a UK trend, with the
OL,7,FWaitrose Food & Drink Report 2023-2024
OL,8,Fsaying that people aged between 18 and
OL,9,F24 are increasingly switching to full-
OL,10,Ffat products.
OL,12,FThe Waitrose report states: "Over the
OL,13,Fpast year, a third of people surveyed
OL,14,Fsaid they have switched from eating a
OL,15,Flow-fat dairy product to a full-fat
OL,16,Fone.
