OL,3,CMore Guernsey islanders are making the
OL,4,Cswitch to full-fat milk
OL,6,FThis was despite 36% of households
OL,7,Fconsuming non-dairy alternatives, an
OL,8,Fincrease from 31% in 2019.
OL,10,FHowever, 15% of islanders were unhappy
OL,11,Fwith the controls on non-Guernsey milk
OL,12,Fimports.
OL,14,FAlmost one in five islanders said
OL,15,FGuernsey milk was not worth the money,
OL,16,Fwith the number of households
OL,17,Fpurchasing Guernsey Cheese falling by
OL,18,F9% since 2019.
